## Design Goal

Create a secure network with:

- Public subnet for internet-facing components
- Private subnet for internal compute
- Controlled outbound access from private subnet

## CIDR Plan

- VPC: 10.0.0.0/16
- Public Subnet: 10.0.1.0/24
- Private Subnet: 10.0.2.0/24

## Why This Design

- Clear separation of exposure
- Reduced blast radius
- Matches real production layouts

